title: CANON PIXMA PRO 100 5d t5 t6i rebel eos canon
description:
HEY THERE, 
 
I have a brand new Canon PIXMA Pro 100 Wireless Professional Inkjet Photo Printer $200 or best offer. Picked up in the Bronx.  
 
The printer is brand new and unopened in the box.  
 
Please note that UPC have been carefully cut from both boxes for rebate purposes. 
 
Thank you 
 
 
============================================================ 
Canon PIXMA PRO-100 Wireless Professional Inkjet Photo Printer features a 4800 x 2400 dpi resolution and Canon's FINE technology with an ink drop as small as 3.0 pl. The printer's 8-cartridge ink system provides a wide color range and includes 3 black inks for high-quality black-and-white photos. The Pro-100 can output borderless prints up to 13 x 19" and is compatible with a wide range of media, including glossy, luster, and matte photo paper as well as Museum Etching and other fine art papers. Additionally, you can print directly on CDs, DVDs, and Blu-ray discs and create your own customizable discs and jackets. The included Print Studio Pro plug in software provides an easy way to achieve optimal results when printing directly from Adobe Photoshop CS and Elements, as well as from Adobe Photoshop Lightroom. 
 
The PIXMA Pro-100 features multiple connectivity options so you can easily print from your different devices. In addition to a standard USB connection, you can connect to the printer over a wired or wireless Ethernet network. Additionally, you can use the front-facing USB port to print directly from a compatible digital camera with PictBridge compatibility. 
 
The PictBridge cable is not included 
 
Print Speeds 
Print an 8.0x10" image in approximately 51 seconds and an 11x14" image in approximately 1 minute 30 seconds 
Canon FINE Technology 
Canon Full-photolithography Inkjet Nozzle Engineering (FINE) features a patented print head that enables printing with microscopic droplets and high resolution up to 4800 x 2400 dpi 
True Monochrome Prints 
The 3 monochrome inks which are part of the 8-ink ChromaLife 100+ system consist of Black, Gray, and Light Gray. These inks deliver enhanced, deep black density to raise your level of professional print quality when creating the dramatic expression of grayscale photography 
Optimum Analysis & Mixture Of Color 
The Optimum Image Generating (OIG) System utilizes two major technologies that were first introduced in the PIXMA PRO-1. The first is a sophisticated mixing balance of inks determined from numerous ink combinations and advanced analysis. During this analysis, the OIG System carefully calculates the best results for each print mode and paper type used while looking at various image factors including color reproduction, tonal gradations, black density, low graininess, glossiness, anti-bronzing and anti-metamerism. These critical ink balancing principles are derived from Canon's expertise in imaging technology, as well as the familiar colors of life that people see and remember on a daily basis. The second is the balancing of color reproduction, tonal gradations, and uniform glossiness. The genius and power of the OIG System is truly showcased when your image is printed, exhibited, and is seen exactly as you envisioned it 
Pro Printing 
The powerful Print Studio Pro plug-in software provides professional photographers effective printing solutions and can directly hand-over image data. Print Studio Pro is compatible with Digital Photo Professional (ver. 2.1 or later), Adobe Photoshop CS, Photoshop Elements, and Photoshop Lightroom 
Built-In CD & DVD Printing 
Conveniently print onto your printable CD, DVD or Blu-ray discs and jackets 
Print Your Vision Up To 13x19" 
Print professional quality photos on various media up to 13x19" 
Versatile Paper Handling 
The 2-way paper feeding provides a rear tray for most supported media types and a dedicated manual feed in the back of the printer for easy loading of thicker papers 
Built-In Wi-Fi 
The built-in Wi-Fi gives you the freedom to place the printer where it's convenient and allows multiple users to seamlessly print from several computers 
Built-in Ethernet Connectivity 
The built-in Ethernet port allows multiple users to seamlessly print from several networked computers in any environment 
Computer-Free Printing 
PictBridge lets you print photos directly from your compatible digital camera, DV camcorder, or camera phone 
Hi-Speed USB 
Plug the cable into your PC for fast data transfer 
AirPrint 
Print photos, email, Web pages and documents from a MacBook, iPhone, iPad, or iPod Touch directly to your printer without installing a driver

title: CANON PIXMA PRO 100 5d t5 t6i rebel eos canon
description:
HEY THERE, 
 
I have a brand new Canon PIXMA Pro 100 Wireless Professional Inkjet Photo Printer $200 or best offer. Picked up in the Bronx.  
 
The printer is brand new and unopened in the box.  
 
Please note that UPC have been carefully cut from both boxes for rebate purposes. 
 
Thank you 
 
 
============================================================ 
Canon PIXMA PRO-100 Wireless Professional Inkjet Photo Printer features a 4800 x 2400 dpi resolution and Canon's FINE technology with an ink drop as small as 3.0 pl. The printer's 8-cartridge ink system provides a wide color range and includes 3 black inks for high-quality black-and-white photos. The Pro-100 can output borderless prints up to 13 x 19" and is compatible with a wide range of media, including glossy, luster, and matte photo paper as well as Museum Etching and other fine art papers. Additionally, you can print directly on CDs, DVDs, and Blu-ray discs and create your own customizable discs and jackets. The included Print Studio Pro plug in software provides an easy way to achieve optimal results when printing directly from Adobe Photoshop CS and Elements, as well as from Adobe Photoshop Lightroom. 
 
The PIXMA Pro-100 features multiple connectivity options so you can easily print from your different devices. In addition to a standard USB connection, you can connect to the printer over a wired or wireless Ethernet network. Additionally, you can use the front-facing USB port to print directly from a compatible digital camera with PictBridge compatibility. 
 
The PictBridge cable is not included 
 
Print Speeds 
Print an 8.0x10" image in approximately 51 seconds and an 11x14" image in approximately 1 minute 30 seconds 
Canon FINE Technology 
Canon Full-photolithography Inkjet Nozzle Engineering (FINE) features a patented print head that enables printing with microscopic droplets and high resolution up to 4800 x 2400 dpi 
True Monochrome Prints 
The 3 monochrome inks which are part of the 8-ink ChromaLife 100+ system consist of Black, Gray, and Light Gray. These inks deliver enhanced, deep black density to raise your level of professional print quality when creating the dramatic expression of grayscale photography 
Optimum Analysis & Mixture Of Color 
The Optimum Image Generating (OIG) System utilizes two major technologies that were first introduced in the PIXMA PRO-1. The first is a sophisticated mixing balance of inks determined from numerous ink combinations and advanced analysis. During this analysis, the OIG System carefully calculates the best results for each print mode and paper type used while looking at various image factors including color reproduction, tonal gradations, black density, low graininess, glossiness, anti-bronzing and anti-metamerism. These critical ink balancing principles are derived from Canon's expertise in imaging technology, as well as the familiar colors of life that people see and remember on a daily basis. The second is the balancing of color reproduction, tonal gradations, and uniform glossiness. The genius and power of the OIG System is truly showcased when your image is printed, exhibited, and is seen exactly as you envisioned it 
Pro Printing 
The powerful Print Studio Pro plug-in software provides professional photographers effective printing solutions and can directly hand-over image data. Print Studio Pro is compatible with Digital Photo Professional (ver. 2.1 or later), Adobe Photoshop CS, Photoshop Elements, and Photoshop Lightroom 
Built-In CD & DVD Printing 
Conveniently print onto your printable CD, DVD or Blu-ray discs and jackets 
Print Your Vision Up To 13x19" 
Print professional quality photos on various media up to 13x19" 
Versatile Paper Handling 
The 2-way paper feeding provides a rear tray for most supported media types and a dedicated manual feed in the back of the printer for easy loading of thicker papers 
Built-In Wi-Fi 
The built-in Wi-Fi gives you the freedom to place the printer where it's convenient and allows mul mputers 
Built-in Ethernet Connectivity 
The built-in Ethernet port allows multiple users to seamlessly print from several networked computers in any environment 
Computer-Free Printing 
PictBridge lets you print photos directly from your compatible digital camera, DV camcorder, or camera phone 
Hi-Speed USB 
Plug the cable into your PC for fast data transfer 
AirPrint 
Print photos, email, Web pages and documents from a MacBook, iPhone, iPad, or iPod Touch directly to your printer without installing a driver

title: GOING OUT OF WEDLOCK SALE - Pottery Barn Bed Set - King
description:
It was his idea.  
 
No, I said. The room's not big enough, I said. But he had the bit between his teeth, and he wasn't letting go. So we bought the king. He got to sleep in his pillow fort. I got to cling to the edge of the bed and not complain when he yanked away the covers. Oh, and guess who got to pay for it? That's right, it's THIS GAL! 
 
Anyway, he's gone, but the bed remains, covered now in dirty laundry, rescue cats and the quickly-dying embers of my middle-aged libido. 
 
Someone please come take it off my hands. I need to downsize. I need to throw off the shackles of this externally-imposed, poor life choice and move on to smaller, greener pastures. 
 
So let's get into it: this, my friends, is an amazing deal! Because this isn't just a king bed, this is a beautiful Pottery Barn king bed plus the two nightstands that go with it, all in excellent condition. This bed is similar to their Hudson bed, though in a white, distressed finish. If you bought the Hudson king-sized bed new right now, it would cost you over $2000 (and that's on sale!) If you went for the matching nightstands, too, you'd be looking at a layout of almost $3000. $3000 just for the bed and nightstands alone! Course, then you'd have to get the mattress, the box spring, the comforter. . . You doing the math here, folks? Cause it is not looking good for Mr. Wallet right now! 
 
However, if you buy this gorgeous, only-a-few-years-old bed, you'll get the frame and the tables for only $1300. And to sweeten the deal, here's what I'm going to toss into the pot. Along with the frame and the nightstands, you'll also get to take home the split box spring (totally encased ever since I had a freak out after reading about the bed bug breakouts a few years ago.) I'll also give you those cute baskets that fit so perfectly in the bottom opening of the nightstands. And to top it off, I'll toss the down comforter into the bargain. (It's from Ikea. Don't remember what unpronounceable string of consonants name they gave it, but I do remember it was the highest grade one available.) 
 
What a deal this is! Seriously, if you're in the market for an inexpensive but beautiful bedroom set, bookmark this page right now. Sure, you can buy a cheap knock-off on Overstock or Wayfair or Walmart. But folks, let me say it again for the back of the class: this is a POTTERY BARN BED -- well-constructed and solid AF. I painted the bedroom recently, and I literally had to use my entire body to move it away from the wall. Indulge in any kinky, Cirque De Sole, acrobatic weird shit you're into on this mother, it can totally take it!  
 
So, ok, let's recap. . . if you go for this showcase, you'll get a beautiful Pottery Barn farm-style king bed in white distressed finish, plus 2 matching nightstands, plus the split box spring, plus the baskets and the Ikea down comforter all for the shockingly low price of $1300! AND, if you act now, I'll throw in 3 Sterilite under-bed storage units. They're 38 x 20, have wheels for easy sliding, open on both sides and fit perfectly under the bed! 
 
For God's sake, how can you even think of walking away?! I know I couldn't... 
 
Well, that's the deal, and an amazing one at that, but just FYI: while I am willing to negotiate, if you're thinking of low-balling me, please don't. Just don't. I'm not in the mood, and I really do need the cash to finance the new, expensive mattress I have to get for my bad back, clearly caused by carrying around all this emotional baggage. (I'm also not interested in selling pieces individually.) 
 
Contact me if you'd like to see it all in person. 
 
(Bedding, duvet cover, pillows, shams, sconces, throws, Ipad, tchotchkes, cute cat and breakfast not included!!!)

title: Knoll Toboggan Chair Desk in Grey
description:
Hi there I'm in the process of moving in the coming weeks and am forced to sell my dear Toboggan Chair-Desk by Knoll.  It is in like new condition, as I've had it for only a few months.  I paid more than 500 bucks and waited 6 weeks for this iconic postmodern work by The Antenna Design Group in New York for Knoll.   My desk is the highly sought after grey on grey version and will underscore the space of its surround with its graceful yet sculptural geometry.   Easy first floor pick up in Park Slope!  
 
If you are interested, PLEASE INCLUDE YOUR NAME AND PHONE NUMBER (FOR TEXT/SMS RESPONSE) IN YOUR FIRST MESSAGE. 
 
Knoll Toboggan is a hybrid object combining a stool and a side table. It doesn't fit into any existing typology as it responds to emerging needs brought about by mobile technology, most notably tablets like the iPad - yet it looks strangely familiar. The shape and scale allows people to shift 360 degrees in the seat, with the curved back serving as backrest, armrest or impromptu tablet work surface. It is light-weight and easy to move around the office for casual get-together.  It's wonderful for the home as well, whether used as casual seating, a work desk, a place of peace and meditation as well as an objet d'art.   Children also love this item as it is a comfortable, modern, bright and slightly ironic take on the traditional notion of a boring mid-century student desk.    Thanks, Otto 
 
Inc. Award for The Best New Office Furniture, August 2012 
Fast Company "A Hybrid Chair-Desk That Fosters Casual Teamwork, July 2012" 
The New York Times "Slipping Into Something More Comfortable, June 2012"

title: Anker Astro E6 Ultra-High Capacity 20800mAh 3-Port 4A Compact Portable
description:
This is a very powerful powerbank that is used to recharge just about any type of usb chargeable device.  I have used this powerbank to recharge the following items: 
 
1) Gopro 
2) A Canon DSLR 
3) iPhone 6 and iPhone 6Plus 
4) Samsung S6 
5) iPad 4 
6) iPad Air 2 
7) Several miscellaneous USB powered devices. 
 
You can recharge an iPhone 6 or 6 Plus or the Samsung S5 or S6 or S7 up to almost 9 times.  So if you have a completely dead iPhone 6Plus you can recharge it from completely dead to full charge almost 9 times (8.8 times to be exact).  I have noticed that the Anker powerbank recharges the device as fast as plugging it into the wall.   
 
You can recharge and iPad Air 2 times with this device again starting from a completely dead iPad Air to full charge. 
It has a Flash light built into it.  At first I did not know why there was a flashlight.  Then I realized how handy that little light came in when I was trying to see to plugin the USB cables when I was in a dark room or going to bed. 
 
The ports on this thing are auto sensing.  This means it can detect a smaller cell phone over the larger ones like the iPhone 6 and iPhone 6 Plus and the Samsung S6.  The auto sensing is key because in most of the other powerbanks on the market it won't auto sense.  This means there may be a single port for 2.1A which is what you want to plugin the larger phones or iPads and get the fast charging.  You can still plugin the same devices I just mentioned to a USB port that is 1.0A but then it would charger alot slower.  This powerbank can sense what device is plugged into any of the 3 ports and it will charge at 2.1A (fast charge).  You can recharge 3 USB devices at once as well as have the powerbank plugged into the wall or computer and recharge the powerbank while you are also recharging the 3 USB devices plugged into the powerbank. 
 
There is a string of LED lights to show you how much charge is left.  Each blue light (there are 4) represents 25% power.  As you recharge the powerbank those lights are lit up and the light will blink until the 25% is charged and it moves onto the next LED until are 4 lights are solid. 
 
 
Check out this Amazon page as that is where I bought it.  I have owned it for about 8 months.  I used it 5 times.   I had to buy a much larger powerbank so that it could recharge my new Surface Pro 4.   
Here is a url to the details of the product.  There are really nice illustrations of this product on Amazon. 
https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B00M2ZNGHU/ref=oh_aui_search_detailpage?ie=UTF8&psc=1 
 
Asking $60.

title: Behringer X32 Mixing Console B-NEW! Authorized Dealer 3-Year Warranty
description:
We also carry Behringer X32 Compact Version, Digital Snake S16, Powerplay P-16M, NU6000 NU46000 PMP4000 PMP6000 X1204USB etc!! 
 
Buy from Authorized Dealer and get the FULL 3-Year Warranty from Behringer 
VISIT OUR SHOWROOM in Queens! 166-05 Jamaica Ave. Jamaica NY 11432 
or call 7I8-29I-I552 
 
 
Product Highlights 
32-channel total recall digital mixer with fully programmable high-end mic preamps and 16 mix buses, configurable as subgroups 
Main LCR and all 16 mix buses feature inserts, 6-band parametric EQ, and dynamics processing 
16 analog XLR outputs plus 6 additional line in/outputs, 2 phones connectors and a talkback section with integrated or external mic 
48-channel digital snake ready* via AES50 ports featuring KLARK TEKNIK's SuperMAC networking capability for ultra-low jitter and latency 
Built-in XUF FireWire/USB audio interface card 
Virtual FX rack featuring 8 true-stereo FX slots for simulations of famous outboard gear 
 
 
The X32 Producer 40-Channel, 25-Bus Digital Mixing Console from Behringer provides a wealth of features in a compact design, ideal for professional live and recording applications. The mixer features 16 fully programmable MIDAS-designed mic preamps. The Main LCR (left, center, right) channels, 16 mix busses, and 6 independent matrix mix busses all have 6-band parametric EQs and integrated dynamics processing for excellent sonic tailoring capabilities.  
 
The mixer has 16 analog XLR outputs, as well as 6 balanced line-level 1/4" Aux inputs and outputs and two 1/4" headphone jacks. The talkback section allows you to communicate with the integrated mic or an external mic. The mixer also has a pair of AES50 ports that feature Klark Teknik SuperMAC networking capability for use with 48-channel digital snakes for ultra-low jitter and latency. The system also has an integrated expansion port that ships with a 32 x 32 XUF FireWire/USB audio card installed. 
 
The built-in Virtual FX offers 8 true-stereo FX slots that deliver high-end simulations of popular processors, such as Lexicon 480L and PCM70, EMT250 and Quantec QRS, etc. The integrated high-power 40-bit floating-point DSP system delivers "unlimited" dynamic range, no internal overload, and near-zero latency between inputs and outputs for top-quality performance. The mixer also has 6 mute groups and 8 DCA groups. 
 
The intuitive interface offers ease-of-use with a dedicated channel strip section that has direct-access controls. There is also a high-resolution 5" color TFT display with associated controls and individual RGB backlit graphic LCDs on every channel. The unit has 17 motorized 100mm faders for extensive user-definable control. 
 
The system has a USB flash connector to provide file storage for uncompressed recordings, show presets, and system updates. There are also connections that support the P-16 personal monitoring system, AES/EBU stereo digital outputs, and MIDI. Adjustable line delays are available on all of the physical inputs and outputs. 
 
Other features of the X32 Producer include networked remote control or show setups with the included remote editor software via USB and Ethernet ports. You can even conveniently handle the scene management duties of complex productions. 
 
Free Control Software Applications 
Behringer iPad and iPhone apps for professional remote operation are free downloads on the Apple App Store. All of the X32's features can be managed concurrently from various locations and instances of the XiQ, XiControl, and XControl apps. 
Versatile and Expandable 
The X32 Producer can act as the nucleus of a flexible and expandable audio system. The built-in 32 x 32 USB recording interface, 8 stereo effects engines, zero-latency monitoring and 100% total recall deliver the tools to handle a wide variety of projects.

title: Firefighter Table Lamp fdny
description:
YOUTUBE VIDEO:  https://youtu.be/eGYf5khkFn8  
 (View above video clip demonstrating the unique way the lamp is turned on.) 
 
What you are looking are handmade fire department SCBA cylinder table and desk lamps. The bottles are 30 minute SCOTT cylinders commonly used in the FDNY and the fire service around the world. The bottles are mounted to the base in the same position it sits on a firefighters back. Two use standard lamp socket and the other a flexible desk lamp. What makes these lamps unique is that in order to turn the light on you spin the cylinder valve and that activates a switch. You can turn the valve either way to to turn it on. I have also added a 4 port USB charge receptacle into the side of the base. The USB charge port is always on as long as the lamp is plugged in. This makes the lamp extremely functional and and quite the attention grabber. The base of this lamp is solid 5/4" oak that has been stained and coated with polyurethane. The overall height is just under 29" and it weighs approximately 17lbs. All lamp bases are made out of oak or mahogany depending on what is available to me. More pictures can be viewed at http://www.fixitkev.com or at Pinterest.com. At the Pinterest site search Fixitkev boards.   
     The lamp would make a great gift for the firefighter in your life, kid or adult.  A dedication plaque can be added to the base to personalize it. One of the photos features a lamp that is on my son's dresser. He loves to show his friends how to turn it on and off. He also likes to be able to charge up his ipad with it.   
     I would be happy to answer your questions or provide information on the different options available with the lamp.  
 
The price is for one lamp only. 
      
 
 
 
 
NO MONEY ORDERS

title: Inspire 1 pro complete drone package like new
description:
I've decided to sell my professional aerial video and photography setup.   Almost 10 grand in hardware.    Call it a drone, quadcopter, whatever....this gets a lot of attention when I bring this out 
 
Inspire 1 pro 
Multiple sets of props 
DBS mods monster 14dBi antenna 
WiFi pro stage 4 antenna cables 
Zenmuse X5 setup 
DJI 15mm f1.7 lens 
Polar pro lens filters (polarized, nd4, UV) 
Olympus 15-45mm zoom lens. (By far my favorite lens) 
DJI balance ring 
Microraptor all-in-one rolling case 
Brand new iPad air 2 (still in the box.  I'm keeping my old one) 
Extra 6dbi antennas 
Remote 4dbi standing antenna 
Lightning and micro USB cables 
16 and 32 GB memory cards 
USB stick for updates 
100w and 180w charger 
2 tb47 batteries 
6 tb48 batteries  
All manuals and paperwork 
 
FULL ASKING PRICE includes my osmo setup and my professional Zoom audio recorder that I use for the audio part of the quad copter video.   Delivery can be included with a fair offer.   Sorry, I will not come to south jersey just to show you it works 
 
 
I've gone 6000 feet with the small antenna and 11000 feet on the big antenna.    Still had full signal and still had several minutes of battery left.  App was modified to run on 32 transmitting channels.   There's definitely a bunch of stuff I'm forgetting to mention but I'll add to this posting as I remember.

The PSR-E353 from Yamaha is 61-touch sensitive key portable keyboard with 550 sounds, 136 accompaniment styles and 102 songs. New in factory (unopened) box Peavey WFS 3.70 Wireless AirPlay active stereo speaker system (Wi-Fi DLNA). 
The WFS 3.70 Wireless AirPlay speaker system is a set of active speakers with AirPlay technology, allowing you to stream music wirelessly from your Mac, PC, iPod touch, iPhone and iPad. 
 
Note: These are not bluetooth. They connect to your Wi-Fi network and devices supporting Airplay will connect to them through the network. They also can be directly connected to either wirelessly (direct connect mode) or through a wired 3.5mm audio jack. 
 
Features 
 
    Active stereo speaker system 
    70W Peak Power Output 
    0.15% Total Harmonic Distortion 
    Woofers: 3" Kevlar cones with dual magnets

    32-bit digital signal processor

title: Behringer X32 Mixing Console B-NEW! Authorized Dealer 3-Year Warranty
description:
We also carry Behringer X32 Compact Version, Digital Snake S16, Powerplay P-16M, NU6000 NU46000 PMP4000 PMP6000 X1204USB etc!! 
 
Buy from Authorized Dealer and get the FULL 3-Year Warranty from Behringer 
VISIT OUR SHOWROOM in Queens! 166-05 Jamaica Ave. Jamaica NY 11432 
or call 7I8-29I-I552 
 
 
Product Highlights 
32-channel total recall digital mixer with fully programmable high-end mic preamps and 16 mix buses, configurable as subgroups 
Main LCR and all 16 mix buses feature inserts, 6-band parametric EQ, and dynamics processing 
16 analog XLR outputs plus 6 additional line in/outputs, 2 phones connectors and a talkback section with integrated or external mic 
48-channel digital snake ready* via AES50 ports featuring KLARK TEKNIK's SuperMAC networking capability for ultra-low jitter and latency 
Built-in XUF FireWire/USB audio interface card 
Virtual FX rack featuring 8 true-stereo FX slots for simulations of famous outboard gear 
 
 
The X32 Producer 40-Channel, 25-Bus Digital Mixing Console from Behringer provides a wealth of features in a compact design, ideal for professional live and recording applications. The mixer features 16 fully programmable MIDAS-designed mic preamps. The Main LCR (left, center, right) channels, 16 mix busses, and 6 independent matrix mix busses all have 6-band parametric EQs and integrated dynamics processing for excellent sonic tailoring capabilities.  
 
The mixer has 16 analog XLR outputs, as well as 6 balanced line-level 1/4" Aux inputs and outputs and two 1/4" headphone jacks. The talkback section allows you to communicate with the integrated mic or an external mic. The mixer also has a pair of AES50 ports that feature Klark Teknik SuperMAC networking capability for use with 48-channel digital snakes for ultra-low jitter and latency. The system also has an integrated expansion port that ships with a 32 x 32 XUF FireWire/USB audio card installed. 
 
The built-in Virtual FX offers 8 true-stereo FX slots that deliver high-end simulations of popular processors, such as Lexicon 480L and PCM70, EMT250 and Quantec QRS, etc. The integrated high-power 40-bit floating-point DSP system delivers "unlimited" dynamic range, no internal overload, and near-zero latency between inputs and outputs for top-quality performance. The mixer also has 6 mute groups and 8 DCA groups. 
 
The intuitive interface offers ease-of-use with a dedicated channel strip section that has direct-access controls. There is also a high-resolution 5" color TFT display with associated controls and individual RGB backlit graphic LCDs on every channel. The unit has 17 motorized 100mm faders for extensive user-definable control. 
 
The system has a USB flash connector to provide file storage for uncompressed recordings, show presets, and system updates. There are also connections that support the P-16 personal monitoring system, AES/EBU stereo digital outputs, and MIDI. Adjustable line delays are available on all of the physical inputs and outputs. 
 
Other features of the X32 Producer include networked remote control or show setups with the included remote editor software via USB and Ethernet ports. You can even conveniently handle the scene management duties of complex productions. 
 
Free Control Software Applications 
Behringer iPad and iPhone apps for professional remote operation are free downloads on the Apple App Store. All of the X32's features can be managed concurrently from various locations and instances of the XiQ, XiControl, and XControl apps. 
Versatile and Expandable 
The X32 Producer can act as the nucleus of a flexible and expandable audio system. The built-in 32 x 32 USB recording interface, 8 stereo effects engines, zero-latency monitoring and 100% total recall deliver the tools to handle a wide variety of projects.

The PIXMA MG3522 Wireless Inkjet Photo All-in-One puts excellent print quality and remarkable convenience in one compact package. title: Beats by Dr. Dre Tour2 In-Ear Headphones, Integrated Remote NEW pix
description:
Beats by Dr. Dre Tour2 Active In-Ear Headphones with Integrated Remote & Mic (Black) - BRAND NEW IN ORIGINAL BOX 
 
​-- ​Powerful bass and high volume without distortion 
-- Compact and portable design 
-- Tangle-free cord 
-- In-line mic and remote to control calls, volume, and tracks 
-- Multiple ear tips for a perfectly sealed fit 
-- Actual cable length: 4.3 ft / 1.3 m 
-- Sweat- and Water-Resistant Design 
-- Optional Wingtips for a Comfortable Fit 
-- Good Sound and Noise Isolation 
-- Full-Range Sound Profile 
-- Integrated Remote & Mic for iOS Devices 
-- Includes Multiple Eartip Sizes 
 
The black Tour2 Active In-Ear Headphones with Integrated Remote & Mic from Beats by Dr. Drecome with a variety of fit options for all-day comfort as you listen to your iPhone or iPad. They provide sweat- and water-resistant protection and deliver a full range of sound wherever your day takes you. 
The headphones can withstand the elements or your toughest workouts. They included multiple sizes of removable wingtips and eartips to provide a versatile fit. Their full-range sound reveals subtle details with crisp highs and powerful lows, and deliver an immersive music experience. 
Furthermore, stay hands-free and control everything at your fingertips with the headphones' tangle-free cable with integrated remote and mic. You can take calls on the go, change volume, and switch tracks without slowing down. The headphones are compatible with iOS devices. 
Compatib​ility:​  iPhone 4 to iPhone 6s Plus; iPad (1st to 3rd generation), iPad with Retina display, iPad mini 1, 2, 3, and 4, iPad Air 1 & 2, iPad Pro (9.7 and 12.9"); iPod classic 80GB/160GB 120GB/160GB (2007 to 2009), iPad nano 1st to 7th generation, iPod shuffle 1st to 4th generation, and iPod touch 1st to 6th generation. 
​ 
B​IG SOUND. SMALL PACKAGE: 
It's rare to find big sound in something so small. Beats Tour earphones are among the first earbuds to hold their own against over ear headphones. Now with a newly designed custom fit and improved sound quality, you can get even closer to the music. 
 
​REDESIGNED FIT: 
​-- ​The perfect listening experience requires the perfect fit. We completely redesigned the Beats Tour and included removable wingtips to provide a customizable fit for precise sound. 
-- Improved Sound​:  While compact and portable, the new Tour is powerful enough to handle all kinds of music. Now you can crank up the volume without distorting the sound. 
-- Tangle-free Cables​:  Doesn't matter how carefully you wind them up, cords and pockets just don't mix. That's why we've redesigned our cables to make sure they're ultra-flexible and tangle-free. 
-- Built-in Mic for Calls​:  Switch easily between songs and incoming calls. No need to take off your Tour to talk into the phone. It's a seamless transition so you can always be on the go. 
 
​IN THE BOX: 
-- Beats Tour earphones 
-- In-ear headphones with inline remote & mic 
-- Soft carry pouch 
-- 4 pairs of ear tips 
-- 3 pairs of secure fit wingtips 
-- Type of jack: 3.5mm 
 
About Beats Audio​:  The company's mission is to provide a superior end-to-end music experience - with headphones, speakers, devices, and services - so fans feel the emotion and hear the music the way artists intended it to sound from the studio. This experience is aided by partnerships with HP, Chrysler Group and HTC Mobile. Led by Co-founder & CEO Jimmy Iovine, Co-founder Dr. Dre, and President & COO Luke Wood, Beats Electronics is based in Santa Monica, CA.

With its high level brand positioning, the company safeguards a heritage of exclusive shoemaking craftsmanship that has become a trademark of a.testoni's quality and style. Today a.testoni is a complex manufacturing company with unique know-how in product research and development and highly contemporary designs. Craftsmanship together with an innovative approach, roots in a historic center of Italian shoemaking and a flair for international entrepreneurship are all elements, consolidated over time, that make a.testoni an exclusive company.

This Blu-Ray Universal Disc player is probably the most well-reviewed, most coveted Blu-Ray or Universal Disc player EVER. Among the formats it is GUARANTEED to play are Blu-Ray, Blu-Ray 3D, DVD, CD, Blu-Ray Audio, SACD and DVD-A. It plays many other formats -- but check online and the manufacturer's specs if you are looking for other specifics. I have personally played all of the above formats and it is spectacular on all of them. Check out the reviews online for yourself. 
 
My favorite features, besides its spectacular visuals and sonics with Blu-Rays, Blu-Ray 3D, DVDs, and its great sound with CDs, SACDs, DVD-As and Blu-Ray Audio are:

description:
Behringer X18 Professional 18-Channel Mixer for IPAD Android Tablet 
UPC: 696859053849 
Visit our showroom to check them out! HOT BEAT 166-05 Jamaica Ave., Jamaica NY 11432 
Call us 7I8-29I-I552 
 
The Behringer X18 - Compact 18-Input Digital iPad/Tablet Mixer is designed for live sound reinforcement and recording applications. The device is designed to sit flat on a surface and features 16 top-facing MIDAS-designed fully programmable microphone preamps via balanced combination Line Level TRS and Microphone XLR-3F connectors, an integrated Wi-Fi module for wireless control from an iPad or tablet, and an 18 x 18 channel bi-directional USB audio interface.  
 
The mixer can be controlled via a free iOS or PC application when connected to an Ethernet, LAN, or Wi-Fi network. Controlling the mixer using a portable device allows you to reference your mix from different listening positions within the venue or studio. The free control app includes four stereo (eight mono) multi-effect processors including delay, chorus, dynamics, 31-band EQ, and simulations of classic analog equipment such as the Lexicon 480L and PCM 80, EMT 250, and Quantec QRS reverbs. The application also includes a 100-band Real Time Analyzer (RTA) for every channel and bus EQ.  
 
The mixer is also capable of sending up to 16 digital sources over CAT5e cable to ULTRANET-compatible devices such as Behringer's P16-M personal monitor mixer for musicians as well as Turbosound iQ loudspeakers for PA applications. Additional I/O include two XLR main outputs, six TRS outputs for auxiliary bus sends, MIDI In, MIDI Out, stereo RCA inputs, stereo RCA outputs, and a headphone output with dedicated level control. You can record your mix via the 18 x 18 USB interface using your digital audio workstation (DAW) of choice. The mixer comes with a copy of Tracktion 4 Audio Production software which provides unlimited track counts, MIDI recording and automation of track dynamics, and support for VST and AU plug-ins.

Best USB mic you will find. 
 
I bought 2 of these Apogee MiC 96k's a year ago from Amazon for $498.08 (total with tax).   Today, the price is still the same on Amazon: 
 
http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B00HHEVL3C/ref=s9_al_bw_g267_i2 
 
As you might expect from an Apogee product - the sound quality is superb.  If you come over to purchase it, I can play you an electronic music track that I made where every single sound used was recorded with this mic (the song isn't released yet so I don't want to post a link here). 
 
As the name suggests, it can record up to 96kHz sample rate.  And the great thing is that it's USB bus-powered.  So you can go on a road trip and have high-quality recordings simply by plugging it into your iPhone, iPad, (or laptop).   They also come with their own little desktop stands, but have a separate extension if you want to mount it onto a real mic stand (see pictures).  More info here:

But, apart from the track I mentioned above, I have barely used them, and I'm realizing that I have too many mic's, and I can't afford to have so many.

OVERVIEW 
 
Apple iPad Pro (9.7in, 128GB, WiFi, Rose Gold) 
Incredibly portable, the 9.7-inch iPad Pro from Apple delivers an unprecedented combination of versatility and performance. At just 0.24" thin and weighing less than a pound, iPad Pro features the brightest, most advanced Retina display ever with True Tone technology which allows the display to match the light around you for a more natural and accurate viewing experience. Powering the 9.7" Retina display is the Apple A9X chip with a M9 motion coprocessor. The 3rd generation 64-bit chip can pump out desktop-class CPU performance and console-class graphics. The faster performance allows you to multitask with ease, using iOS 9 features, such as Picture in Picture, Slide Over, and Split View. The 12MP iSight camera can shoot Live Photos and even record in 4K video. It also has 1080p slow-motion video support. The front-facing 5MP camera allows you to FaceTime in HD and it also has a True Tone software flash for a more natural-looking selfie. Four integrated speakers produce an innovative stereo soundstage as enveloping as its display. Apple's iPad Pro uses Touch ID technology to turn your fingerprint into an unforgettable password so you can unlock your device with just a touch. You can also make secure purchases in iTunes, iBooks, and the App Store. And with Apple Pay, you can make purchases within your apps easily and securely. Enjoy ultrafast WiFi connectivity and up to 10 hours of battery life. Storage Capacity: 128GB. Finish: Rose Gold. 
 
System Requirements: Apple ID (required for some features); Internet Access. Mac: OS X v10.8.5 or later; PC: Windows 7 or later. Syncing with iTunes on a Mac or PC requires iTunes 12.3 or later. 
 
Protect your iPad Pro with the included tablet case from Tucano. Constructed from soft eco leather, this case has a water-repellent finish. The tablet can be switched on and off by opening/closing the cover. The front cover converts into a handy stand with infinite viewing and writing positions. When you want to take a quick photo or video, the foldable flap allows quick access to the camera. Color: Black.
